{"tid":1760035,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐港公署發表聲明：美方倒行逆施將遭到包括香港同胞在內的全體中國人民的迎頭痛擊！","createTime":"2019-11-28T03:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T03:24:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc049eddd2be33245cb939bb2190b8e0e4da9e3","tid":1760035,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:12:08.000Z","msg":"11月28日，美行政當局簽署所謂&ldquo;香港人權與民主法案&rdquo;等，嚴重干預香港事務和中國內政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。外交部駐港公署予以強烈譴責，表示堅決反對！<br />\n<br />\n  聲明表示，美方所謂法案顛倒黑白，充斥強盜邏輯，就是縱容暴力犯罪，就是要毀掉香港，破壞&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;，就是要阻撓中國人民實現偉大復興，但這是徒勞的，是癡心妄想。包括香港同胞在內的中國人民不答應！國際社會也不答應！<br />\n<br />\n  聲明強調，香港是中國的香港，香港事務不容任何外部勢力染指，中國內政不容任何外國干涉。中國政府維護國家主權、安全、發展利益的決心堅定不移，貫徹&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;方針的決心堅定不移，反對任何外部勢力干預香港事務的決心堅定不移。美方倒行逆施將遭到包括香港同胞在內的全體中國人民的迎頭痛擊！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fmcoprc.gov.hk/chn/gsdzywtdbthlc/t1719798.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmcoprc.gov.hk%2Fchn%2Fgsdzywtdbthlc%2Ft1719798.htm&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=0fc60bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fmcoprc.gov.hk/chn/gsdzywtdbthlc/t1719798.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n今日既第三篇聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2596102b0237a86cacacddd72140fbd9ea6f7f","tid":1760035,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:15:35.000Z","msg":"又係果三個堅定不移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁堅定不移唔好傾貿易協議啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6f473f67be33b3a7bbd3e7064f8b1d044227ca","tid":1760035,"uid":337608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6hrnuf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6hrnuf.png&h=be785f4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a6deb15eb1f12d45280